â€” The genus 
<taxonomicName id="51CD2ABCFF95DF30FBA3C80623FFB20A" authorityName="Osborn" authorityYear="1901" box="[1113,1208,319,342]" class="Insecta" family="Saldidae" genus="Saldoida" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="335" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
