<bibRefCitation id="F25C2CCEFF95DF30FB8CC8472254B2CA" author="Cobben, R" box="[1142,1299,382,406]" pageId="6" pageNumber="335" pagination="3 - 30" refId="ref9245" refString="Cobben, R. H., 1987. New African Leptopodomorpha (Heteroptera: Saldidae, Omaniidae, Leptopodidae), with an annotated checklist of Saldidae from Africa. II. New taxa of Saldidae (except the genus Saldula), Omaniidae, Leptopodidae, and a checklist of African shorebugs. Revue de Zoologie Africaine, 101: 3 - 30." type="journal article" year="1987">Cobben (1987)</bibRefCitation>
